===================

RAILWAYS WELCOME
INT'L TRADE, TOURISM
#- LAMBAT CITY —  The Government of Lambat has opened its first railway station in Central County, Lambat city. The station is connected to the underground Appomattoxan line at 7000 longitude, which has access to the Nexus, a major transport hub.

#- Meanwhile, the government has begun constructing the East-West Overground Railway (EWOR), which seeks to link Lambat City to New Athol, a new settlement in Impor.
These transport projects aim to reduce domestic and international travel time, 
#- and to provide a safe route to citizens and travellers alike. Ω
==================
ICENIA DECLARES VICTORY VS. RAIDERS

ICENIA  — After  two days of fighting a raider group, the Icenian government has declared victory and said  
#- their country is safely welcome to visitors.
The combined forces of the Icenian Militia, the UDF, and the Coalition battled against the invasion. This group of raiders included EZ2Clutch and  chosentwice. 

#- PvPers alleged to be members of another Civ server also participated in the offensive, although this was denied by some members of the raider group. Ω

===================
#- ===================




